    parentName: "p"
  }), "\n", "As if by magic - or do I actually have navigation skills? - I found the junction. I was pretty proud of myself. As a total orientation dead loss... If I leaned my bike against a tree against the direction of travel, after peeing, I no longer knew where I had come from.", mdx("br", {
    parentName: "p"
  }), "\n", "But was this junction such a good idea? The road was small and pretty bad. There was a slope of 14%, I got scared of heights - already! To be on the safe side, I rode downhill as slowly as the rode bike cyclists coming uphill.", mdx("br", {
    parentName: "p"
  }), "\n", "The west wind (we are big friends) came up again after a week's break. Fresh and steady, he cooled my sunburned faces. Was just there, just like me, only a few billion years older. No reason to chafe.", mdx("br", {
