    parentName: "blockquote"
  }, "Suddenly I was in the last village 20 km before the pass: Borce, very pretty, splendid view, St. Jacques Museum with a lovely pilgrim hostel in it. It cost \u20AC11.80, though. I could park my bike and Jaqueline warm and dry inside. I went in and unpacked, was the only one. Great, so I could wash my stuff.", mdx("br", {
    parentName: "p"
