    parentName: "p"
  }), "\n", "Today I put my backpack on my back because it was easier to ride uphill. At breakfast I wrote a birthday card. As I cycled through the next village, Urdos, the last French village, I posted it in the mailbox. You can always find one in France, even in the most remote place.", mdx("br", {
